- if @domains.any?
  .mt-4.p-3.font-lusitana.rounded-t-lg.bg-mauve-300
    The list of root domains used in
    %strong= @exercise.name
    environment. Subdomains can be created and bound to networks to create a hiearchy.

  .bg-white.dark:bg-gray-800.grid.grid-cols-3.p-4.gap-2= render collection: @domains, partial: 'domains/card', as: :domain

- else
  = render Emptylisting::Component.new(klass: Domain)
